high_descs: Walk to the counter ahead to the right of the toaster.
Pick up the gray plate to the right of the lettuce.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Put the plate inside of the fridge on the second shelf.
Pick up the tomato to the left of the lettuce on the top shelf.
Put the tomato on the gray plate on the second shelf.
anns.task_desc: To move a gray plate to the fridge, and put a tomato on the plate.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge, and put the plate in the fridge.
Put the tomato on the plate in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a tomato on a plate in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward a step, turn right, go forward to the counter.
Take the plate from the counter.
Turn around, go forward to the fridge.
Put the plate on the lower shelf of the fridge.
Take the tomato from the fridge.
Put the tomato on the plate in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate in a fridge and put a tomato on the plate.
